EASY INVOICE PDF, is an application that is simple and inexpensive, to solve all of your billing problems.

In few minutes you can create an invoice and send it via email to your customer, you can also download the invoice directly to your computer via ITUNES, then print it or to create a backup file of your invoices.

The simplicity of this application for iPod touch & IPHONE lets you create an invoice in no time directly from your customer.

This application was born from an experience from well 15 years experience in creating software for small and medium enterprises. 

This application works in the languages: ENGLISH, ITALIAN, FRENCH, SPANISH, GERMAN.

TECHNICAL FEATURES:
-customer management;
-Manage categories;
-Management Products;
-Billing Management;
-Email delivery Management;
-File sharing Management with iTunes;
-Euro & Dollar Management;
-Invoice Manage up to 6 simultaneous VAT rates;
-Preview of the invoice;
-Viewing PDFs created;
-Possibility to place products in real-time on invoices;
-Managing Archive Invoices;
-Ability to insert a comment;
-Withholding tax Management;

